.8]}, {"text": "6.5", "bbox": [823.4, 682.0, 849.4, 702.8]}, {"text": "2.2", "bbox": [917.2, 682.0, 943.2, 702.8]}, {"text": "14.4", "bbox": [1000.6, 682.0, 1037.0, 702.8]}, {"text": "730.8", "bbox": [1094.4, 682.0, 1141.3, 702.8]}, {"text": "Total Contractual Cash", "bbox": [232.4, 715.4, 426.1, 736.2]}, {"text": "Obligations . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [253.3, 740.4, 474.2, 761.2]}, {"text": "$2,006.2", "bbox": [495.1, 740.4, 568.0, 761.2]}, {"text": "$1,067.0", "bbox": [588.9, 740.4, 661.8, 761.2]}, {"text": "$2,182.2", "bbox": [682.7, 740.4, 755.6, 761.2]}, {"text": "$4,328.3", "bbox": [776.5, 740.4, 849.4, 761.2]}, {"text": "$3,659.7", "bbox": [870.3, 740.4, 943.2, 761.2]}, {"text": "$9,733.3", "bbox": [964.1, 740.4, 1037.0, 761.2]}, {"text": "$22,976.7", "bbox": [1057.9, 740.4, 1141.3, 761.2]}, {"text": "(1)", "bbox": [190.7, 794.6, 215.0, 815.4]}, {"text": "The tranche E term loans mature in May 2025, the tranche F term loans mature in June 2023, and the", "bbox": [232.4, 794.6, 1076.1, 815.4]}, {"text": "tranche G term loans mature in August 2024. The term loans require quarterly principal payments totaling", "bbox": [232.4, 819.6, 1118.6, 840.4]}, {"text": "$19.1 million.", "bbox": [232.4, 844.6, 350.0, 865.4]}, {"text": "(2)", "bbox": [190.7, 869.6, 215.0, 890.4]}, {"text": "The 2022 Notes will be fully redeemed in the first quarter of fiscal 2020 in connection with the issuance of", "bbox": [232.4, 869.6, 1125.0, 890.4]}, {"text": "$2,650.0 million of new 2027 notes. Since this transaction occurred after September 30, 2019, it is not", "bbox": [232.4, 894.6, 1086.6, 915.4]}, {"text": "reflected in the contractual obligations table.", "bbox": [232.4, 919.6, 604.9, 940.5]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [190.7, 944.6, 215.0, 965.5]}, {"text": "Assumes that the variable interest rate on our tranche E, tranche F and tranche G borrowings under our", "bbox": [232.4, 944.6, 1091.7, 965.5]}, {"text": "Senior Secured Term Loans range from approximately 4.7% to 5.0% based on anticipated movements in the", "bbox": [232.4, 969.6, 1137.6, 990.5]}, {"text": "LIBO rate. In addition, interest payments include the impact of the existing interest rate swap and cap", "bbox": [232.4, 994.6, 1081.6, 1015.5]}, {"text": "agreements described in Note 21, “Derivatives and Hedging Activities” to the consolidated financial", "bbox": [232.4, 1019.7, 1071.4, 1040.5]}, {"text": "statements herein.", "bbox": [232.4, 1044.7, 383.2, 1065.5]}, {"text": "In addition to the contractual obligations set forth above, the Company incurs capital expenditures for the", "bbox": [232.4, 1088.2, 1113.0, 1109.1]}, {"text": "purpose of maintaining and replacing existing equipment and facilities and, from time to time, for facility", "bbox": [190.7, 1113.2, 1072.0, 1134.1]}, {"text": "expansion. Capital expenditures totaled approximately $101.6 million, $73.3 million, and $71.0 million during", "bbox": [190.7, 1138.2, 1115.2, 1159.1]}, {"text": "fiscal years 2019, 2018, and fiscal 2017, respectively. The Company estimates its capital expenditures in fiscal", "bbox": [190.7, 1163.3, 1115.8, 1184.1]}, {"text": "year 2020 to be between $160 million and $190 million with the increase from previous years attributable to the", "bbox": [190.7, 1188.3, 1126.8, 1209.1]}, {"text": "Esterline businesses being under TransDigm ownership for the entire fiscal year period.", "bbox": [190.7, 1213.3, 923.8, 1234.1]}, {"text": "Off-Balance Sheet Arrangements", "bbox": [190.7, 1265.9, 486.2, 1286.7]}, {"text": "The Company utilizes letters of credit to back certain payment and performance obligations. Letters of", "bbox": [232.4, 1300.4, 1089.2, 1321.2]}, {"text": "credit are subject to limits based on amounts outstanding under the Company’s revolving credit facility. As of", "bbox": [190.7, 1325.4, 1109.0, 1346.3]}, {"text": "September 30, 2019, the Company had $41.5 million in letters of credit outstanding.", "bbox": [190.7, 1350.4, 894.6, 1371.3]}, {"text": "New Accounting Standards", "bbox": [190.7, 1403.0, 433.9, 1423.9]}, {"text": "For information about new accounting standards, see Note 4, “Recent Accounting Pronouncements,” to our", "bbox": [232.4, 1437.5, 1129.8, 1458.4]}, {"text": "consolidated financial statements included herein.", "bbox": [190.7, 1462.6, 607.8, 1483.4]}, {"text": "48", "bbox": [655.6, 1512.9, 676.4, 1533.7]}]}